{"tid":2080142,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"姚手足 9.14 普通襲擊罪不成立 官：撐警漢施襲在先","createTime":"2020-06-26T08:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T23:43:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":550,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"4d3966f0abd592cbd7f49965221ee28805625980","tid":2080142,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:30:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200626/MP63VBM5WOGVSG7EIX4CSC76EA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2FMP63VBM5WOGVSG7EIX4CSC76EA%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=190e0c88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2FMP63VBM5WOGVSG7EIX4CSC76EA%2F&h=ee83df66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200626/MP63VBM5WOGVSG7EIX4CSC76EA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u06zV6r0iDvthsyLNeonIC3wR8w=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G47LK6Y7KETJBNGODLJNNX5EVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu06zV6r0iDvthsyLNeonIC3wR8w%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG47LK6Y7KETJBNGODLJNNX5EVI.jpg&h=c00546c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年輕舞台燈光設計師去年在將軍澳欲向路障投擲汽油彈圖阻警方前進，早前認罪，判囚四年。他另涉一案，被指於案發前一個月在淘大花園附近「連儂牆」與人爭執，其間涉襲擊一名撐警中年漢。案件早前審結，裁判官屈麗雯今裁決時指，被告當時遭事主捉住並扯下頭套，事主的動作「有敵意、迅速、突然、有力，情緒不見得冷靜」，被告實是受到事主「襲擊」，不能排除被告是以合理武力自衞，裁定被告罪名不成立。"},{"pid":"41d12606ba9bf18e38e1f9b281420d3bd07671d7","tid":2080142,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:31:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ae66f301c7809dc2976a19b15f52c4a936774612","tid":2080142,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41d12606ba9bf18e38e1f9b281420d3bd07671d7","tid":2080142,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":